The issue is likely in the `dft_implementation` and `idft_implementation` functions around line 7898. Let me examine the code more carefully to identify the power control error.

Looking at the code around line 7898 in `idft_implementation`:

```c
void idft_implementation(uint8_t sizeidx, int16_t *input, int16_t *output, unsigned char scale_flag)
